content:
As an AI language model, I don't monitor internet or other sources to be up-to-date with new start-ups, but there have been numerous interesting startups that have emerged in recent years. Here are a few examples:

1. Impossible Foods - This startup is dedicated to creating plant-based meat substitutes that are both delicious and sustainable.

2. Peloton - A fitness startup that creates at-home exercise equipment and provides virtual workout classes.

3. Airbnb - A platform that allows travelers to find unique and affordable accommodations around the world.

4. Robinhood - An investment app that allows users to invest in the stock market with no fees.

5. Zoom - A video conferencing platform that has become essential for remote work and virtual events during the pandemic.

These are just a few examples, and there are many more fascinating startups out there!
